<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Greška u serveru | Mesec Od Papira</title>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="js/fontawesome.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="js/common/script.js" defer></script>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/common/style.css">
    <style type="text/css">
		.wrapper{
			position: relative;
			min-height: 100%;
		}
        .card{
            position: relative;
            top: 50%;
    		left: 50%;
    		padding: 20px;
    		width: 450px;
    		transform: translate(-50%, 50%);
    		justify-content: center;
    		text-align: center;
			line-height: 20px;
			font-family: poppins, sans-serif;
    		border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    		border-radius: 10px;
    		background: var(--card-background);
    		color: var(--txt-color);
    		animation: articleLoad 0.5s ease-in 0.5s;
    		animation-fill-mode: forwards;
    		opacity: 0;
    		transition: all 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        .card h1{
            margin-top: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
			text-align: center;
			letter-spacing: 1px;
            font-family: Optima, sans-serif;
            font-size: 52px;
            color: var(--txt-color);
            animation: headerLoad 0.5s ease-in 0.5s;
            animation-fill-mode: forwards;
            transform: translateY(-20px);
            opacity: 0;
        }
        .card p{
            margin-top: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
			font-size: 16px;
            color: var(--p-color);
        }
        .card button{
            cursor: pointer;
		    position: relative;
		    width: 175px;
		    height: 30px;
			border: none;
			border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 15px;
		    background: #007bf6;
		    color: white;
		    transition: all 0.25s ease-in-out;
        }
		.footer{
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            padding: 16px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 50px;
			text-align: center;
			font-family: Optima, sans-serif;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            background: var(--card-background);
			color: var(--p-color);
    		transition: all 0.5s ease-in-out;
        }
        .footer-left{
			display: flex;
            position: absolute;
			left: 15%;
        }
        .footer-right{
			display: flex;
            position: absolute;
            right: 15%;
        }
		.footer i{
			width: 20px;
			height: 100%;
			font-size: 20px;
		}
        @media screen and (max-width: 1024px){
			.card{
				width: 70%;
				transition: all 0.5s ease-in-out;
			}
            .footer{
                font-size: 12px;
                height: 75px;
            }
    		.footer-left{
    		    left: 0;
				right: 0;
				margin-left: auto;
				margin-right: auto;
				width: 200px;
            }
            .footer i{
                font-size: 15px;
            }
    		.footer-right{
                position: relative;
				top: 25px;
 				left: 0; 
 				right: 0; 
 				margin-left: auto; 
 				margin-right: auto; 
 				width: 300px;
    		}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body<%- mode %>>
    <div class="container">
	    <div class="logo">
	    <img src="logo/mop.png" onclick="window.location.href = '/'">
	    	<h4 onclick="window.location.href = '/'">Mesec Od Papira</h4>
	    </div>
		<nav>
			<div class="search">
				<form class="searchBox" action="/pretraga" method="GET">
					<input onkeyup="searchResults()" class="input" type="text" placeholder="Pretraži..." name="q">
					<table class="search-results"></table>
					<button class="searchBtn" type="button"></button>
				</form>
			</div><% if(token == true){ %> 
			<%- include('../partials/admin/_nav') %> 
			<% }else{ %> 
				<ul class="links">
					<li><a href="/">Početna</a></li>
					<li><a href="/poezija">Poezija</a></li>
					<li><a href="/o-meni">O meni</a></li>
					<li onclick="switchMode();" style="position: absolute; right: 70px"><i class="fas fa-adjust" id="dark-mode-toggle"></i></li>
				</ul>
<%}%><div class="mobile">
				<div class="line1"></div>
				<div class="line2"></div>
				<div class="line3"></div>
			</div>
		</nav>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="card">
                <h1>500</h1>
                <p>Žao nam je, došlo je do greške u serveru.<br><br> Pokušajte osvežiti stranicu ili kontaktirajte administratora ako se greška nastavi.<br>
                </p>
                <a href="/"><button>Nazad na početnu</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
		<div class="footer">
			<div class="footer-left">
				Copyright &copy;<script type="text/javascript">document.write(`&nbsp${new Date().getFullYear()}&nbsp`)</script><a href="/">Mesec Od Papira</a>
			</div>
			<div class="footer-right">
				Designed, developed and distributed by&nbsp;<a href="https://www.instagram.com/velickovicdj/" style="display: inherit;"><i class="fa fa-instagram"></i>velickovicdj</a>
			</div>
		</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>